{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532940/extras/Steam-CTA-v2-C.gif?t=1732957553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ardaria will be a survival-creative game on a procedural voxel planet that you can fully terraform. Face brutal creatures in gore PvE fights with melee and magic. Build your character, choose skills and stats which match your play style. Explore monuments and villages populated with NPCs.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532940/extras/stylized-hr.png?t=1732957553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The creative mode gives you the most freedom you ever experienced in creative with an integrated schematic import / export feature to share your creations with the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Download it now and build something impressive !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532940/extras/stylized-hr.png?t=1732957553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upcoming features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crafting and Job System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Resource Mining</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Agriculture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Automation and Logic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">RPG - Skills and Stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">NPCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tame and Ride Majestic Mounts </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532940/extras/stylized-hr.png?t=1732957553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532940/extras/ardaria-build-mode-showcase.jpg?t=1732957553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\